{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":103333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[25],"categories_output":[{"ID":25,"slug":"%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e7%90%90%e7%a2%8e","name":"生活琐碎","term_taxonomy_id":25,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":30}],"tags":[64,65,39],"tags_output":[{"ID":64,"slug":"%e5%8a%a8%e6%bc%ab%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb","name":"动漫动画","term_taxonomy_id":64,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":65,"slug":"%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e6%84%9f%e6%83%b3","name":"生活感想","term_taxonomy_id":65,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":39,"slug":"%e7%bd%91%e9%a1%b5%e8%ae%be%e8%ae%a1","name":"网页设计","term_taxonomy_id":39,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":25}],"thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_4b3b336293b94a173481ac72-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombbbaacxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_4b3b336293b94a173481ac72-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombbbaacxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_4b3b336293b94a173481ac72-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombbbaacxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_full":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_4b3b336293b94a173481ac72-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombbbaacxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"date_day":"26","date_month":"09","date_month_e":"September","date_year":"2011","date_weekday":"Monday","title":"5年至今，到底有什么一直没变","excerpt":"2007年至今，到底有什么一直没变....","content":"<p><span>2007年至今，到底有什么一直没变....</span></p>\n<p><strong>1.发型</strong>。从高中二年级，就被小混混朋友带着到处“改造”，试过不下10种发型，最终发现，只适合，而且只能保持，这种动漫版的自己设计的发型</p>\n<p><strong>2.体重</strong>。一直就是那么几斤，吃多点就重点，吃少点就轻点。运动量大点就轻点，工作量大点就重点，总之，0.5 KG&lt;差值&lt;3KG</p>\n<p><strong>3.爱好</strong>。从6岁开始，直至现在，动漫动画和手柄游戏一直是痴迷的。 跳舞，设计，一直是几年爱好和追求的东西</p>\n<p><strong>4.理想</strong>。心中的那个一定要实现，而且必须实现的小小理想，一直没有变过</p>\n<p><strong>5.饮食</strong>。巧克力，纯牛奶</p>\n<p><strong>6.帆布鞋</strong>。身体的其他部分无所谓，鞋子，匡威帆布鞋的穿戴率达到了95%以上，不为什么，只因为它是比较耐磨的运动类帆布鞋了</p>\n<p><strong>7.DIY</strong>。文具盒里的3只DIY自制动漫水性笔。一直用它们记学习笔记，记录职业规划，乱七八糟的东西。还有记录一些梦到的东东。</p>\n<p><strong>8.性格</strong>。对职业上，对未来上，对喜欢的人爱的人，对动漫，那种既好又不好的傻冒性格，让我成为真实的我</p>\n<p>没有了……..</p>\n<p></p>\n","slug":"9088c7a0c717397130871062","prev":[{"ID":83333,"title":"鱼鱼的TA，你能遇到吗？","excerpt":"鱼鱼的TA，经常爱隐藏着心里的一丝悲伤，在你的面前依然绽放笑容，不是TA勉强，不是TA坚强，是TA懂得取舍，懂得理解！","slug":"67dae24d52e56fbda883460c","post_date":"2011-08-28 21:04:09","post_date_gmt":"2011-08-28 21:04:09","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_09172392e01de1faf7a79779-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomedefafaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_09172392e01de1faf7a79779-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomedefafaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_09172392e01de1faf7a79779-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomedefafaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":53333,"title":"分享一些我设计和创意时常去的国外灵感站","excerpt":"在进行一个设计需求调研和创作方案的这段时间，肯定很多时候是参考各种资料和网站。而我，更喜欢参考一些国外的东东，下面就对我常去的一些灵感站做一些分享。","slug":"dde3e8c095b453069d114e5a","post_date":"2011-10-17 04:53:23","post_date_gmt":"2011-10-17 04:53:23","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_36bfd7e7391734a341e3cb00-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombfdeaecbxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_36bfd7e7391734a341e3cb00-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombfdeaecbxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_36bfd7e7391734a341e3cb00-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombfdeaecbxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"post_date":"2011-09-26 01:36:35","post_date_gmt":"2011-09-26 01:36:35","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2011-09-26 01:36:35","post_modified_gmt":"2011-09-26 01:36:35","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"https://matrixflip.com/api/?post_type=post&amp;p=103333","menu_order":0,"post_type":"post","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","filter":"raw"}},"__N_SSG":true}